sentences: Park Yun-ha (Korean: 박윤하; born April 23, 1991), better known by her stage name Giant Pink, is a South Korean rapper.
Giant Pink married a younger businessman in November 2020.
On December 6, 2021, she announced that she is pregnant after a year of marriage.
